milestones.description: Sajjad Ahmed and Habibul Bashar's 28-run partnership is BAN's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 26 between Azhar Hossain and Gazi Ashraf
Khaled Mashud has broken the record for most dismissals in an innings (2) in ODIs for BAN, going past Hafizur Rahman's 1
Akram Khan has broken the record for most catches in an innings (2) in ODIs for BAN, going past Raqibul Hasan's 1
Minhajul Abedin has become the top wicket-taker for BAN in ODIs with 6 wickets, going past Gholam Nousher's 5
Akram Khan has broken the record for most catches (4) in ODIs for BAN, going past Azhar Hossain's 2
